The paper discusses a platform that uses machine learning techniques to ingest and extract data from scientific articles and technical literature. This falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) as the platform aims to make the content of these documents discoverable. Additionally, the use of machine learning techniques suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), deep learning (cs.DL), machine learning (cs.LG), and computer vision (cs.CV).
